      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The flight to Lisbon is smooth. We both manage to sleep a little and the hours fly by. Once again I’m plagued by whatever trashy thing the person in front of me is watching, unable to look away. With no sound I’m forced to fill in the blanks of a show that I can only imagine is Forrest Gump meets Bridgerton. (The show turns out to be called Ghosts). ",
            "link": null
          },
